data.description: This home is in pristine condition with a floor plan that just makes sense! The main floor offers beautiful maple Hardwood floors, formal living room, updated open concept kitchen with brand new Quartz countertops, beautiful backsplash and stainless-steel appliances and tons of storage, spacious living and dining room, mudroom, and half bath. The second floor offers an extra-large primary bedroom with a huge bathroom and large walk-in closet, 3 additional rooms, full bathroom, and laundry room with folding bench. Huge highlight to this home is the fully finished basement with crawlspace for even more storage and 2 additional rooms with closets that can be great for anything to include bedrooms, home gym, or office. The privacy-fenced backyard with two large decks and fire-pit is great for entertaining your family or guests. Don't miss the chance to make this your dream home. Schedule your showing today! (Broker Owned)
